{"tid":2238063,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐國聯即時討論區","createTime":"2020-10-10T20:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T09:32:42.000Z","uid":13106,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca6ed6288d52a225f26b42210f98593cb144cca0","tid":2238063,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T20:07:43.000Z","msg":"唔好意思呃咗大家入嚟 希望咁多位波台手足可以放低成見 齊心簽歐洲國家嘅聯署 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n零德文 30秒註冊兼簽埋!<br />\n點解今次聯署咁重要？簽滿5萬人，德國國會就一定要開聽證會展開聆訊<br />\n10月20日截止，而家仲要多二萬幾個簽名<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-itm1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/120954983_182280763472854_7953286082107751083_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=7rv_RrpB07MAX9axTyd&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-itm1-1.xx&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=c5660ccd7e023dfe337cb06deb1f312e&amp;oe=5FA62613\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-itm1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F120954983_182280763472854_7953286082107751083_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3D7rv_RrpB07MAX9axTyd%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-itm1-1.xx%26tp%3D14%26oh%3Dc5660ccd7e023dfe337cb06deb1f312e%26oe%3D5FA62613&h=dc1bafea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次個中文版將繁複嘅步驟嘅變到簡單易用，送到埋口啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">1. 去 <a href=\"http://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=cc5032c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://act4hk.com/petition</a></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-itm1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/121148649_182280833472847_4518489040676640905_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=5dke8DvFiLQAX8Nw8VO&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-itm1-1.xx&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=c2a87e1065ec54cc0928b934fd9b6d17&amp;oe=5FA53469\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-itm1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F121148649_182280833472847_4518489040676640905_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3D5dke8DvFiLQAX8Nw8VO%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-itm1-1.xx%26tp%3D14%26oh%3Dc2a87e1065ec54cc0928b934fd9b6d17%26oe%3D5FA53469&h=0c11a55c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">2. 展開詳情後揀註冊並聯署（第一次簽德國聯署嘅話）</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-itm1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/121062864_182280796806184_7676295957470484568_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=YURK8GXu4hcAX8ru7GW&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-itm1-1.xx&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=c1cf7df9c6cd6ba25a4d570d2b2ebb43&amp;oe=5FA5F56B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-itm1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F121062864_182280796806184_7676295957470484568_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DYURK8GXu4hcAX8ru7GW%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-itm1-1.xx%26tp%3D14%26oh%3Dc1cf7df9c6cd6ba25a4d570d2b2ebb43%26oe%3D5FA5F56B&h=31752afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">3. 填名同email，act4hk幫你註冊</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fkix2-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/120906751_182280770139520_7971181035828545653_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=bRrD6R-6Dz4AX9lJBu6&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fkix2-2.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=7960d6632bc69923fe9c2cb1d3f3354a&amp;oe=5FA6E7DD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fkix2-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F120906751_182280770139520_7971181035828545653_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DbRrD6R-6Dz4AX9lJBu6%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fkix2-2.fna%26tp%3D14%26oh%3D7960d6632bc69923fe9c2cb1d3f3354a%26oe%3D5FA6E7DD&h=0e217ad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">4. 開email會收到驗證email</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-itm1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/121091278_182280873472843_1201602866671510778_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=egn5yNxQObwAX8SpS75&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-itm1-1.xx&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=83282b5dd963e5a697cf857b94d36e5e&amp;oe=5FA7A270\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-itm1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F121091278_182280873472843_1201602866671510778_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3Degn5yNxQObwAX8SpS75%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-itm1-1.xx%26tp%3D14%26oh%3D83282b5dd963e5a697cf857b94d36e5e%26oe%3D5FA7A270&h=d6a8e83c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">5. 如圖示㩒驗證link</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-itm1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/121094459_182280840139513_7447325289835237778_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=XPj4suaVLk0AX-bWkN-&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-itm1-1.xx&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=f22a20e56f69f676f758958bc82c0879&amp;oe=5FA559A4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-itm1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F121094459_182280840139513_7447325289835237778_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DXPj4suaVLk0AX-bWkN-%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-itm1-1.xx%26tp%3D14%26oh%3Df22a20e56f69f676f758958bc82c0879%26oe%3D5FA559A4&h=ad231320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">6. Act4hk自動填咗你啱啱登記嘅電郵同密碼，只需㩒「簽署請願書」。禮成</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-itm1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/120943779_182280813472849_5971889361022879124_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=hdTx7x7zojMAX_uo_MI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-itm1-1.xx&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=cbeead42b71dac4e74bc4dedc1b007fb&amp;oe=5FA62520\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-itm1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F120943779_182280813472849_5971889361022879124_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DhdTx7x7zo